text: Lansing Kill flows into the Mohawk River in Hillside, New York. Pixley Falls is a waterfall located on Lansing Kill by Hurlbutville, New York. Lansing Kill flows through Pixley Falls State Park and it flows parallel to the old Black River Canal for much of its course. == References == , Category:Rivers of Oneida County, New York Category:Mohawk River
title: Lansing Kill (Mohawk River tributary)
